JDBC is JAVA DETABASE CONECTIVITY it is used to connect with database
and excute the sql querys with the help of JDBC API.

JDBC is a API (application programming interface) used in java programming
to interact with databases.

types of drivers FOUR:

1.odbc Driver
2.native-api Driver
3.network protocol Driver
4.thin Driver

that is u must know the theory of JDBC API for Interview.
 